Name: IMPOSSIBALL
About the game: IMPOSSIBALL is a silly and strange adventure made by a two man team where you must rescue 'The Golden pin' from the clutches of evil whilst traveling through time. Take on many difficult levels such as *The Wild West *An Ancient Temple *A Pirate Ship *A Cyberpunk City *Outer Space *A Medieval Town And Many More! In IMPOSSIBALL you play as a red Bowling ball that won't stop rolling and you must avoid whatever obstacles are thrown your way!
